  {"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["# AksaraDetect - Full Project di Google Colab\n\n**Sebelum mulai:**\n1. Klik **Runtime** → **Change runtime type** → pilih **T4 GPU** → Save\n2. Ganti GANTI_API_KEY_KAMU di Cell 3 dengan API key Roboflow kamu\n3. Ganti GITHUB_USERNAME di Cell 2 dengan username GitHub kamu\n4. Klik **Runtime** → **Run all**\n5. Tunggu ~15 menit, lalu klik URL yang muncul di Cell terakhir"]},
  {"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Cell 1 - Install semua dependensi"]},
  {"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["!nvidia-smi\n!pip install ultralytics roboflow streamlit pyngrok PyYAML matplotlib seaborn pandas Pillow scikit-learn -q\nprint(\"Install selesai!\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},
  {"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Cell 2 - Clone project dari GitHub"]},
  {"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# Clone project dari GitHub\n!git clone https://github.com/GITHUB_USERNAME/aksara-detect.git /content/app\nprint(\"Project berhasil di-clone!\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},
  {"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Cell 3 - Download dataset dari Roboflow"]},
  {"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["from roboflow import Roboflow\nimport yaml, os\n\n# Ganti dengan API key dari app.roboflow.com -> Settings -> API\nAPI_KEY = \"GANTI_API_KEY_KAMU\"\n\nrf = Roboflow(api_key=API_KEY)\nproject = rf.workspace(\"novalrizkiansyah-ymail-com\").project(\"aksara-ulu-rejang\")\ndataset = project.version(4).download(\"yolov8\")\n\nDATA_YAML = dataset.location + \"/data.yaml\"\nbase = os.path.dirname(DATA_YAML)\n\nwith open(DATA_YAML) as f:\n    data = yaml.safe_load(f)\n\ndata[\"train\"] = base + \"/train/images\"\ndata[\"val\"]   = base + \"/valid/images\"\ndata[\"test\"]  = base + \"/test/images\"\n\nwith open(DATA_YAML, \"w\") as f:\n    yaml.dump(data, f)\n\nprint(f\"Dataset siap! {data[\"nc\"]} kelas\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},
  {"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Cell 4 - Training YOLOv8 (GPU ~10 menit)"]},
  {"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["from ultralytics import YOLO\n\nmodel = YOLO(\"yolov8n.pt\")\nresults = model.train(\n    data     = DATA_YAML,\n    epochs   = 50,\n    imgsz    = 640,\n    batch    = 32,\n    device   = 0,\n    project  = \"/content/runs\",\n    name     = \"aksara_ulu\",\n    exist_ok = True,\n)\nprint(\"Training selesai!\")\nprint(\"mAP50:\", results.results_dict.get(\"metrics/mAP50(B)\"))"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},
  {"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Cell 5 - Setup model & label map"]},
  {"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["import os, json, shutil, yaml\n\n# Buat folder yang dibutuhkan\nfor d in [\"/content/app/models\",\"/content/app/results\",\"/content/app/logs\"]:\n    os.makedirs(d, exist_ok=True)\n\n# Copy model terbaik\nshutil.copy(\"/content/runs/aksara_ulu/weights/best.pt\", \"/content/app/models/best.pt\")\n\n# Buat label_map.json\nwith open(DATA_YAML) as f:\n    d = yaml.safe_load(f)\nlabel_map = {str(i): name for i, name in enumerate(d[\"names\"])}\nwith open(\"/content/app/models/label_map.json\", \"w\") as f:\n    json.dump(label_map, f, indent=2)\n\nprint(\"Model & label map siap!\")\nprint(f\"Labels: {len(label_map)} kelas\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},
  {"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Cell 6 - Update config untuk Colab"]},
  {"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# Update config.py agar path sesuai Colab\nconfig_content = """import os\nBASE_DIR         = \"/content/app\"\nDATA_YAML        = \"\" + DATA_YAML_PATH + \"\"\nMODEL_DIR        = \"/content/app/models\"\nRESULT_DIR       = \"/content/app/results\"\nLOG_DIR          = \"/content/app/logs\"\nRUNS_DIR         = \"/content/app/runs\"\nMODEL_BEST_PATH  = \"/content/app/models/best.pt\"\nMODEL_LAST_PATH  = \"/content/app/models/last.pt\"\nLABEL_MAP_PATH   = \"/content/app/models/label_map.json\"\nMETRICS_PATH     = \"/content/app/models/metrics.json\"\nPREDICT_LOG      = \"/content/app/logs/prediction_log.json\"\nCONF_THRESHOLD   = 0.25\nIOU_THRESHOLD    = 0.45\nAPP_NAME         = \"AksaraDetect\"\nAPP_VERSION      = \"1.0.0\"\nAPP_TAGLINE      = \"Aksara Ulu Rejang - YOLOv8\"\n"""\n\nDATA_YAML_PATH = DATA_YAML\nconfig_content = config_content.replace(\"DATA_YAML_PATH\", f\"\\\"{DATA_YAML}\\\"\")\n\nwith open(\"/content/app/src/config.py\", \"w\") as f:\n    f.write(config_content)\n\nprint(\"config.py diupdate!\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},
  {"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Cell 7 - Jalankan GUI Streamlit"]},
  {"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["import subprocess, time, sys\nfrom pyngrok import ngrok\n\n# Jalankan streamlit\nproc = subprocess.Popen(\n    [sys.executable, \"-m\", \"streamlit\", \"run\",\n     \"/content/app/src/app.py\",\n     \"--server.port\", \"8501\",\n     \"--server.headless\", \"true\",\n     \"--server.enableCORS\", \"false\",\n     \"--server.enableXsrfProtection\", \"false\"],\n    cwd=\"/content/app/src\"\n)\n\ntime.sleep(8)\n\n# Buat URL publik\ntunnel = ngrok.connect(8501)\nprint(\"=\" * 55)\nprint(\"AKSARADETECT SIAP!\")\nprint(f\"Buka URL ini: {tunnel.public_url}\")\nprint(\"=\" * 55)\nprint(\"(URL aktif selama session Colab berjalan)\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]}
 ]
}
